snippet.title: Tere Bin Ep 14 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 14 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 9th February 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

snippet.title: Kudiyee Ni Teri (Selfiee) – Akshay Kumar | Mrunal Thakur | The PropheC | Tanishk B | Zahrah S Khan
snippet.description:
Star Studios presents in association with Dharma Productions, Prithviraj Productions, Magic Frames & Cape Of Good Films.

A Dharma Productions Film SELFIEE

Starring Akshay Kumar, Emraan Hashmi, Nushrratt Bharuccha, Diana Penty
Directed by Raj Mehta
Produced by Hiroo Yash Johar, Aruna Bhatia, Supriya Menon, Karan Johar, Prithviraj Sukumaran, Apoorva Mehta & Listin Stephen
Screenplay and Dialogues by Rishhabh Sharrma
Music Supervised by Azeem Dayani

All Streaming Links : https://ingrooves.lnk.to/KudiyeeNiTeri

Credits
Song: Kudiyee Ni Teri
Featuring: Akshay Kumar & Mrunal Thakur
Singers: The PropheC  and Zahrah S Khan  
Original Music: The PropheC
Recreation by: Tanishk Bagchi
New Lyrics by: The PropheC and Tanishk Bagchi
Mix and Master: Eric Pillai @ Future Sound of Bombay
Music Supervisor: Azeem Dayani
Song Director : Ahmed Khan
Choreographer : Prince Gupta
Associate Music Supervisor: Megha Vikaas Bali

Special Thanks: Sumeet Kr Tyagi

Play Desi Music Factory 
Founder & CEO - Anshul Garg 
Play dmf project head   - Raghav Sharma 
Label manager - Gaurav Bharti  
Playdmf team - Gaurav Arora, Asheema Chauhan & Sankalp Garg 
Special thanks - Rajat Nagpal
Special Thanks: Ingrooves Team https://www.ingrooves.com/ 
Digital Promotions - Net Media


Lyrics :📝

Kitta takni ne tang jad takeya, 
Tu chain mera leya billo kho, 

Rag rag vich khoon wang wagdi ae, 
Dhadkan karan kive slow, 

Dil vich ni tu tak tak kardi, 
Choran wangu thugdi ae tu, 
Kachi daru wang sir nu tu chad di, 
Sohni aini lagdi tu, 


Akh main soniye jadon di tere naal layi ayi ayi, 
Gaya sab kujj lutt channiye, 
Tere bina na koi hor dil ch aayi aayi aayi, 
Ki kargi ae tu balliye, 

Kudiye ni teri vibe aa 
Mainu khiche tere nehde, 
Laavan tere ni main gede,
Jad kardi tu vibe, Munda karda na lie, 

Kudiye ni teri vibeaa 
Kitta mainu ni tabah,
Hoya firda shadayi, Teri vibe, 
Baitha dil ch basayi, 

Seene vich tere dil mera dhadke
Mere dil vich yaara dhadke tu

Lakh lakh tenu yaar manavan
Kyun na manaven tu mainu

Teri tor te ishaareyan ne maare munde,
 Aewein sanu piche naiyo layida, 

Jad nikle tu agg niri ban ke, 
Ni aewein dil nu ni tadfayida, 

Jhillon di akhan jiwein hon talvaran, 
Mere kol jad langdi tu, 

Kude tu chaddiyan ne sab piche naaran,
Agge saareyan ton nikli tu, 

Kudiye ni teri vibe, 

Mainu khiche tere nehde, 
Laavan tere ni main gede, Jad kardi tu vibe, 
Munda karda na lie, 

Kudiye ni teri vibe, 
Kitta mainu ni tabah, 

Hoya firda shadayi, Teri vibe, 
Baitha dil ch basayi, 

Soneya ve akhiyan tainu,
Tak tak rende ne

Na ve kateya ek pal
Yaara tere bin


Sareyanu karda ae vibe
Ki kareya ve tera mera vibe

Kaisa he yeh tere mera vibe
Ki kareya ve tera mera vibe


Kudiye ni teri vibe aa 
Mainu khiche tere nehde, 
Laavan tere ni main gede,
Jad kardi tu vibe, Munda karda na lie

#AkshayKumar #Selfee #MrunalThakur

snippet.description:
Presenting you the Official Trailer of #Dhanush in & as #Vaathi! #VaathiTrailer

Vaathi / SIR is an upcoming Tamil/Telugu bilingual film written & directed by Venky Atluri. Music is composed by GV Prakash Kumar & Cinematography is handled by J Yuvraj. Sithara Entertainments headed by Suryadevara Naga Vamsi will be co-producing this film along with Sai Soujanya (Fortune Four Cinemas). The film is Presented by Srikara Studios.

Starring: Dhanush, Samyuktha
Co-Starring: Sai Kumar,Tanikella Bharani,Samuthirakani,Thotapalli Madhu, Narra Srinivas, Pammi Sai, Hyper Aadhi, Shara, Aadukalam Naren, Ilavarasu, Motta Rajendran, Hareesh Peradi, Praveena & Others.

snippet.title: Turkey Earthquake: Operation Dost के तहत तुर्की की मदद कर रही Indian Army और NDRF की टीमें
snippet.description:
#turkey #operationdost #livehindustan  
तुर्की और सीरिया में आए भीषण भूकंप के चलते 15 हजार से अधिक लोगों की मौत हो गई। दुनिया भर से आए बचाव दल वहां मदद के लिए चौबीसों घंटे काम कर रहे हैं। इस संकट की घड़ी में भारत सरकार ने भी तुर्की की ओर मदद का हाथ बढ़ाया है। भारत की तरफ से Operation Dost के तहत मानवीयता के आधार पर बचाव अभियान चलाया जा रहा है। आइए जानते हैं क्या है Operation Dost…

snippet.title: Tere Bin Episode 15 Teaser - 9th February 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 15 Teaser - 9th February 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

snippet.title: Tere Bin Ep 13 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Nisa BB Cream - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 13 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa BB Cream - 8th February 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally presented by Nisa BB Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim

snippet.title: Indian Army's 'We Care' message wins hearts in Turkey; Woman kisses soldier, picture goes viral
snippet.description:
India's 'Operation Dost' is underway in full swing in Turkey as the Indian Army pushes forward with search, rescue and relief operations. India has emerged as a quick responder to the devastation in Turkey and Syria after a 7.8 magnitude earthquake hit the two countries on February 6. The Indian Army team has set up a field hospital in Turkey's Hatay which is fully functional with running medical, surgical and emergency wards. So far, India has sent six flights with search and rescue teams, dog squads, medicines and medical equipment. The death toll from the catastrophic earthquake has risen to over 17,500.

#turkey #india #turkeyearthquake #indiaaid #indianarmy #operationdost #indiaturkey #syria

snippet.title: Turkey-Syria earthquake: Buildings crumble as deadly earthquakes hit
snippet.description:
Footage shows the terrifying moment a 7.8 magnitude earthquake hit Turkey and Syria, crumbling buildings and killing thousands of people.

snippet.title: Mixing All Brand Biryani to Make A Super Biryani | Taste Test
snippet.description:

chhan chhan Jo baje ghar mein aisi meri chij tu la de ,

banke Tu thanedar se Laye Rakhe Meri Pessi
Main M.A Angreji Thi , Balam Mane Mil Gaya Desi

snippet.title: Sankar ने बनाई Tina से छुटकारा पाने की योजना | Thapki Pyar Ki |थपकी प्यार की |Full Episode | Ep. 618
snippet.description:
Sankar ने बनाई Tina से छुटकारा पाने की योजना | Thapki Pyar Ki | थपकी प्यार की | Full Episode | Ep. 618

Tina gets into trouble when she is caught eavesdropping on Shraddha and Sankar's conversation. Shraddha decides to get rid of Tina. Will she be successful? Meanwhile Thapki's plan to keep Bihaan's revived memory a secret is off to a good start. Bihaan's willingness to marry Sankar is the first step of their plan. Will their plan reach fruition? 

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3689 - 8 Feb 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3689: Bagha Ki Laparvahi
--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide was trying to listen to Tapu Sena's talk in order to learn more about the intricacies of the surprise present because he was fascinated by it. The Mahila Mandali are advised to use "Nimbu Mirchi" on their doors by the grocer of the Gokuldham society since a ghost has been skulking around in the nearby societies. The Mahila Mandal rejects the rumor and believes it to be a ruse to get rid of all the lemons. Jetha, on the other hand, becomes irate when he can't locate the crucial document in the file and reprimands Bagha for letting Bawri into the store during working hours. Stay tuned to find out! 

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3689, 8 Feb 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000208755

snippet.title: Vani Jairam -ன் மனதை நெகிழ வைக்கும் கதை | வாணி ஜெயராம் | Tamil Glitz.
snippet.description:
‘ஏழு ஸ்வரங்களின் கான சரஸ்வதி’ என்றும்  ‘கலையின் நாயகி’ என்றும் போற்றப்படும் வாணி ஜெயராம் ..
‘ஏழு ஸ்வரங்களுக்குள் ஒரு வாணி’யாக  கலைவாணி என்ற இயற்பெயருடன் பிறந்தார்..
‘எல்லா மொழிகளிலும் அதன் சிறப்பு குறையாமல் உச்சரிக்கும் வல்லமை பெற்ற வாணி ஒரு ஆயுட்கால பாடகியே’- என்று கவிஞர் கண்ணதாசனால் பாராட்டப்பட்டவர் vani Jayaram..
இசைப்புயல் ஏ.ஆர்.ரகுமான் தனக்கென சொந்தமாக இசைக் குழு ஒன்றை ஆரம்பித்தபோது அந்த இசைக்குழுவை குத்துவிளக்கேற்றி தொடங்கி வைத்தவர் vani jairam.
19 மொழிகளில் சுமார் 20 ஆயிரத்துக்கும் மேற்பட்ட பாடல்களை பாடி சாதனை படைத்த  ஒரே பாடகி vaani jayaram.
3 தேசிய விருதுகள் 3 ஃபிலிம்ஃபேர் விருதுகள் கலைமாமணி விருது பத்ம பூசன் விருது போன்ற எண்ணற்ற விருதுகளை பெற்றுள்ள  ..
வாணி ஜெயராமின் திரையிசைப் பயணம் என்பது ..எழுதி முடிக்க முடியாத பல சாதனைகளை உள்ளடக்கியது. 
வாணி ஜெயராம் இந்திய சினிமாவுக்கு கிடைத்த மிகவும் அரிதான ஒரு பொக்கிசம் என்றே சொல்லலாம்.

‘எல்லா மொழிகளிலும் அதன் சிறப்பு குறையாமல் உச்சரிக்கும் வல்லமை பெற்ற வாணி ஒரு ஆயுட்கால பாடகியே’- என்று கவிஞர் கண்ணதாசனால் பாராட்டப்பட்டவர் vani Jayaram..
இசைப்புயல் ஏ.ஆர்.ரகுமான் தனக்கென சொந்தமாக இசைக் குழு ஒன்றை ஆரம்பித்தபோது அந்த இசைக்குழுவை குத்துவிளக்கேற்றி தொடங்கி வைத்தவர் vani jairam.
19 மொழிகளில் சுமார் 20 ஆயிரத்துக்கும் மேற்பட்ட பாடல்களை பாடி சாதனை படைத்த  ஒரே பாடகி vaani jayaram.
3 தேசிய விருதுகள் 3 ஃபிலிம்ஃபேர் விருதுகள் கலைமாமணி விருது பத்ம பூசன் விருது போன்ற எண்ணற்ற விருதுகளை பெற்றுள்ள  ..
வாணி ஜெயராமின் திரையிசைப் பயணம் என்பது ..எழுதி முடிக்க முடியாத பல சாதனைகளை உள்ளடக்கியது. 
வாணி ஜெயராம் இந்திய சினிமாவுக்கு கிடைத்த மிகவும் அரிதான ஒரு பொக்கிசம் என்றே சொல்லலாம்.

snippet.title: Unseen Passage In English | Class 10/12 |Comprehension Passages Tricks |CBSE English Class 10th 12th
snippet.description:
Attention all Class 10th and 12th students!
Recently cbse has changed the style of English Question paper where Unseen passage has also seen some significant changes .The new pattern focuses on analysing student's competency that has made this topic a little complicated.
